2015年1月6日，来自[[达吉斯坦共和国|达吉斯坦]]的戴安娜·拉玛佐诺娃在[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]市中心[[苏丹艾哈迈德_(法蒂赫)|苏丹艾哈迈德]]地区，[[蘇丹艾哈邁德清真寺|蓝色清真寺]]和[[圣索菲亚大教堂|圣索菲亚大教堂]]附近的一个警察局引爆了身上的炸弹背心。拉玛佐诺娃在袭击中丧生并造成两名警官受伤，其中一人后来经抢救无效死亡。<ref name="BBC1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30701483|title=BBC News - Turkey bombing: Female suicide attacker hits Istanbul police station|date=2015-01-06|work=BBC新闻|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830023657/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30701483|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AJ1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/01/policeman-injured-istanbul-bomb-attack-20151615551340942.html|title=Policeman killed in Istanbul suicide attack|date=2015-01-06|work=半岛电视台|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2016-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804223603/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/01/policeman-injured-istanbul-bomb-attack-20151615551340942.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉玛佐诺娃是一名寡妇并怀有身孕，她的丈夫是挪威-车臣籍的伊斯兰国战士，2014年12月在叙利亚被杀害。
== 袭击 ==
伊斯坦布尔省省长沙欣({{lang-tr|Vasip Şahin}})说，该名女子的英语有“浓重的口音”，并穿着[[尼卡布|尼卡布]]，在引爆炸弹之前她进入警察局，并告诉警察说她丢失了钱包。<ref name="BBC1"/>[[土耳其总理列表|土耳其总理]][[艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢|艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢]]告诉记者，袭击者还携带了另外两个爆炸装置，警察在现场安全地拆除了。爆炸现场附近的公共服务采取了紧急措施，通过该地区的有轨电车电缆被临时停电。<ref name="AJ1"/>除了施襲者，有一人在袭击中死亡，是一名来自[[特拉布宗|特拉布宗]]的年轻警务人员，他刚刚做了父亲。

== 凶手 ==
袭击发生后，警方拘留了六个人，其中包括三名外国人。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2015/Jan-13/283951-turkey-detains-six-over-istanbul-suicide-bombing.ashx?utm_source=Magnet&utm_medium=Entity%20page&utm_campaign=Magnet%20tools|title=Turkey detains six over Istanbul suicide bombing|accessdate=2015-09-22|date=2015-01-13|work=[[每日星报_(黎巴嫩)|每日星报 (黎巴嫩)]]|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129234333/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2015/Jan-13/283951-turkey-detains-six-over-istanbul-suicide-bombing.ashx?utm_source=Magnet&utm_medium=Entity%20page&utm_campaign=Magnet%20tools}}</ref>

1月7日，极左武装组织[[革命人民解放黨-陣線|革命人民解放黨-陣線]]（DHKP/C）声称对此次袭击负责，说这是“惩罚杀害[[贝尔金·埃尔万|贝尔金·埃尔万]]（{{lang|tr|Berkin Elvan}}）的凶手”和“打倒腐败的正义与发展党（AKP）保护的法西斯杀人犯、盗窃部长”。15岁的男孩贝尔金·埃尔万在[[2013年土耳其反政府抗议运动|2013年伊斯坦布尔的抗议活动]]中被一名警察发射的催泪瓦斯罐击中昏迷，2014年3月死亡。<ref name="AJ1"/> 此次袭击发生的五天前（1月1日），另一名DHKP/C成员袭击了[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]时代的[[多爾瑪巴赫切宮|多爾瑪巴赫切宮]]外站岗的警察，投掷的两枚手榴弹没有爆炸。该建筑是土耳其总理驻伊斯坦布尔的办公室。<ref name="自由每日新闻">{{cite news|title=DHKP-C claims Istanbul palace attack bid|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/dhkp-c-claims-istanbul-palace-attack-bid.aspx?pageID=238&nid=76412|accessdate=2016-08-31|publisher=自由每日新闻|date=2015-01-02|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911110513/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/dhkp-c-claims-istanbul-palace-attack-bid.aspx?pageID=238&nid=76412|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该组织还称，自杀式爆炸者是Elif Sultan Kalsen。后来前往刑事医疗中心辨认尸体的Kalsen家人对此予以否认，指出这不是他们的女儿。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/leftist-group-carried-istanbul-suicide-bombing-28048471|title=Leftist Group Says It Carried out Istanbul Suicide Bombing|accessdate=2015-01-08|author=Butler, Desmond|date=2015-01-07|publisher=[[ABC新闻|ABC新闻]]|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225063349/https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/leftist-group-carried-istanbul-suicide-bombing-28048471%20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月8日，凶手被确认为是戴安娜·拉玛佐诺娃，来自[[达吉斯坦共和国|达吉斯坦]]的俄罗斯车臣公民。她在2014年与来自车臣的挪威公民Abu Aluevitsj Edelbijev结婚。他们在进入叙利亚之前，从2014年5月到7月在伊斯坦布尔待了三个月。在叙利亚Edelbijev为伊斯兰国战斗并被杀害。拉玛佐诺娃在此时怀孕，在她丈夫死亡不久后非法潜返土耳其。<ref>Toygun Atilla (2015-01-16) [http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/suicide-bomber-who-attacked-istanbul-police-was-married-to-norwegian-isil-jihadist.aspx?PageID=238&NID=77070&NewsCatID=509 Suicide bomber who attacked Istanbul police was married to Norwegian ISIL jihadist] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/suicide-bomber-who-attacked-istanbul-police-was-married-to-norwegian-isil-jihadist.aspx?PageID=238&NID=77070&NewsCatID=509 |date=20160807170031 }} Hürriyet</ref><ref name="guardian-article">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jan/16/pregnant-istanbul-suicide-bomber-russian-citizen|title=Pregnant Istanbul suicide bomber was Russian citizen|accessdate=22 September 2015|author=Letsch, Constanze|date=2015-01-16|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004220022/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jan/16/pregnant-istanbul-suicide-bomber-russian-citizen|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/27918961.asp|title=Canlı bombanın El Kaide ve IŞİD bağlantısı araştırılıyor|accessdate=2015-01-08|publisher=[[自由_(土耳其媒体)|自由 (土耳其媒体)]]|language=tr|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109223735/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/27918961.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="daily-news1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/russian-citizen-revealed-to-be-suicide-bomber-who-attacked-istanbul-police.aspx?pageID=238&nID=76653&NewsCatID=509|title=Russian citizen revealed to be suicide bomber who attacked Istanbul police|accessdate=2015-01-08|author=Aydın, Çetin|date=2015-01-08|publisher=[[自由每日新闻|自由每日新闻]]|archive-date=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108141305/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/russian-citizen-revealed-to-be